pful in the interpretation of\nother types of supernovae, particularly those that are not well characterized,\nsuch as extremely luminous supernovae and faint fast objects.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Aug 2016 20:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-15"}
