fic\nnetwork topology. These result suggest a much richer dynamics of memristive\nnetworks than previously considered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Aug 2016 20:32:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Oct 2016 10:55:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 2 Nov 2016 10:46:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-08"}
